      • tutorialUpdate

        public boolean tutorialUpdate(GameItem g,
                              int drawHeight,
                              boolean clicked)
        tutorialUpdate: handles logic for updating game while in tutorial mode
        Parameters:
        g - - the current GameItem drawn on screen which needs to be updated
        drawHeight - - y-location of where objects disappear from screen
        clicked - - boolean saying whether or not the item in question has been clicked (info is retrieved from MouseListener in View)
        Returns:
        false, to reset the boolean value in View
